{"tid":208052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方深水埗搗破網上百家樂賭檔","createTime":"2017-04-19T09:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T10:06:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b66c53827a35be2c3adbb48cdc3532d28a17f3df","tid":208052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"AM730<br />\n<br />\n警方深水埗搗破網上百家樂賭檔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方根據線報，昨晚約10時，突擊搜查深水埗醫局街124號一個單位，搗破網上百家樂賭檔， 5女1男被捕，年齡21至57歲，其中1名女子涉嫌經營賭博場所，1名男子涉嫌協助經營賭博場所，其餘人士就涉嫌在賭博場所內賭博，全部人正被扣留調查。行動中，檢獲約3萬元賭款、約50萬元籌碼、一部電腦及一部電視。警方初步調查，相信賭檔已運作約2星期。"},{"pid":"be31b896ef391c65e95f15bcf43675b39877bc9e","tid":208052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"破獲一台麻雀雀友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64dc04f705ff087d4977102a42332d612987c15","tid":208052,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"上線啦"},{"pid":"0b3d8fa08a45f7e4f775926c4f98a88401296ebc","tid":208052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上線啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a42ed73923aac62768e23fa151de23d2e735d9","tid":208052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上線啦</blockquote><br />\n免費av 就係咁嚟"},{"pid":"341af286223332ab0728f639bea5a0cd584d7f36","tid":208052,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"內文冇講喇，如果佢喺明網開賭場咁就真係超級大傻仔啦"},{"pid":"885ec90da2b2ed5e96a2f2ee520df18802b3cb79","tid":208052,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09: